title: Fitbit Flex 2 – Fashion & Fitness
description: Fitness is now in fashion with the all-new Flex 2 — a swim-proof fitness wristband with an ultra-slim removable tracker that fits inside bands, bangles or pendants, so you can automatically track all-day activity, exercise and sleep in a style that’s all your own.
